% Add "sync" flag so you can just read and write the database

.state todo
.date 2026-03-17 20:58:52-03:00
.tags

It's usefull when you have an old db version and you want to save to the latest version of the database but
you don't want to do any write operations.
It'll just load the db and write it to the last version.

